288
00:09:40,997 --> 00:09:44,125
[ volume increases ]

289
00:09:44,209 --> 00:09:45,335
[ gasps ]

290
00:09:45,418 --> 00:09:47,337
Jake, what are you doing?

291
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:49,005
Oh, hey, guys.

292
00:09:49,089 --> 00:09:51,091
I'm just sharing a tender moment

293
00:09:51,174 --> 00:09:53,551
with my beautiful friend, Tiffany.

294
00:09:53,635 --> 00:09:55,845
Stop! You're making Lady jealous.

295
00:09:55,929 --> 00:09:58,056
Well, I'm trying to make you both jealous.

296
00:09:58,139 --> 00:10:00,350
Why would | be jealous of Tiffany?

297
00:10:00,433 --> 00:10:03,937
Because Tiffany's a boy!

298
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:05,730
sENIEREREREL

299
00:10:05,814 --> 00:10:08,942
Jake's my best friend now -- forever.

300
00:10:09,025 --> 00:10:10,026
[ gasps ]

301
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:10,944
[ growls ]

302
00:10:11,027 --> 00:10:13,780
Yah!

303
00:10:14,864 --> 00:10:17,450
Homewrecker!

304
00:10:18,493 --> 00:10:21,496
Jake, what's going on with you?

305
00:10:21,579 --> 00:10:23,123
Oh, | guess I'm jealous

306
00:10:23,206 --> 00:10:25,291
of how much you and Finn
like each other.

307
00:10:25,375 --> 00:10:26,751
I'm hanging out with Finn

308
00:10:26,835 --> 00:10:29,546
because you wanted us to get to know
each other better.

309
00:10:29,629 --> 00:10:31,589
| know. Ugh!

310
00:10:31,673 --> 00:10:34,134
Get out of my life, Tiffany,
and never come back!

311
00:10:34,217 --> 00:10:37,262
Oof! No! Jake will be mine!

312
00:10:37,345 --> 00:10:40,098
I'm sorry I'm an idiot, baby.
Forgive me?

313
00:10:40,181 --> 00:10:43,017
Oh, sweet potato, | love you
because you're an idiot.

314
00:10:43,101 --> 00:10:45,270
You make me feel like a genius.

315
00:10:45,353 --> 00:10:46,187
[ both laugh ]

316
00:10:46,271 --> 00:10:49,190
You make me feel like
I'm hugging an old man.

317
00:10:49,274 --> 00:10:51,401
It's time to get rid of
this piece of crud.

318
00:10:51,484 --> 00:10:52,777
[zap!]
Aah!

319
00:10:52,861 --> 00:10:53,736
[ chuckles ]

320
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:54,821
[ speaks Korean ]

321
00:10:54,904 --> 00:10:56,281
Yeah, way better.

322
00:10:56,364 --> 00:10:57,699
FINN:
Beat it, Tiffany!

323
00:10:57,782 --> 00:10:58,867
Go on -- get.

324
00:10:58,950 --> 00:11:01,411
You'll never defeat me!

325
00:11:01,494 --> 00:11:06,457
| will be Jake's best friend
because I'm Tiffany!

326
00:11:06,541 --> 00:11:08,293
Aaaaaah!

327
00:11:08,376 --> 00:11:10,753
I'm sorry | was an idiot.
You forgive me?

328
00:11:10,837 --> 00:11:12,797
Shut up, man.
| don't want to hear that stuff.

329
00:11:12,881 --> 00:11:14,424
Let me get in there.

330
00:11:14,507 --> 00:11:16,426
Let's never be stupid again.

331
00:11:16,509 --> 00:11:17,343
Wait.

332
00:11:17,427 --> 00:11:19,262
Let's a/ways be stupid -- forever.

333
00:11:19,345 --> 00:11:20,763
Amen.

334
